#+TITLE: ShapelessOS Package Manager
Org-Mode Based System

* Overview

The ShapelessOS Package Manager is an org-mode based system for managing packages through literate documentation. It combines:
- Full documentation (LFS-style depth)
- Automatic Guix package generation
- Git-based source tracking with automatic hash computation
- Emacs integration for smooth workflow
- Stow management for FHS compatibility

* Architecture

#+BEGIN_SRC
Org-Mode Package Definition (YOU write this)
    ↓
MAAK Parser (extracts metadata + code)
    ↓
Git Fetch + Hash Computation (automatic)
    ↓
Guix Package Generation (reproducible build)
    ↓
Build to /gnu/store (immutable)
    ↓
Stow to /usr (FHS compatibility)
    ↓
Package Available System-Wide
#+END_SRC

